Sixteen new cases of Coronavirus (COVID-19) have been reported in Nigeria: 10 in Lagos, 2 in the FCT, 2 in Oyo, 1 in Delta and 1 in Katsina According to NCDC, as at 09:30 pm, 7th April there are 254 confirmed cases of COVID-19 reported in Nigeria. 44 have been discharged with six deaths. Details: 254 confirmed cases
